1. *Istorija* je nauka koja se bavi proučavanjem prošlih događaja. (History is a science that studies past events.)
2. U školi učimo o istoriji Srbije. (*Istorija* - genitive, In school we learn about the history of Serbia.)
3. *Istoriju* umetnosti volim više od istorije politike. (I like art history more than political history.)
4. Ovaj grad ima bogatu *istorijsku* prošlost. (This city has a rich historical past.)
5. *Istorija* će suditi o našim postupcima. (History will judge our actions.)
6. Na fakultetu sam izabrala da studiram *istoriju*. (I chose to study history at university.)
7. *Istorijat* ove firme datira još od 19. veka. (The history of this company dates back to the 19th century.)
8. Kada putujem, volim da posetim muzeje i istorijske spomenike. (When I travel, I like to visit museums and historical monuments.)
9. *Istorija* se ponavlja, kažu. (They say that history repeats itself.)
10. Pročitao sam knjigu o *istorijskim* bitkama. (I read a book about historical battles.)